<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="running-adj">running <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'rʌnɪŋ/    美 /'rʌnɪŋ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>[只用于名词前] 奔跑的；赛跑的；用于赛跑的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a running train 
行进中的列车</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>running shoes
跑鞋</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>流动的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>running water</strong> 
自来水；流水</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a fast-running river 
湍急的河流</p></div></div>